node.text: I realize a lot of people who follow me on here don’t know my story. I highly recommend watching the whole thing on @revamppedpodcast, as I spill all the tea on my Youtube journey, struggles and wins over the years. Here’s small snippet of my story of moving to the US and chasing the American dream. Enjoy!
